with Simon, so...

14:12.332 --> 14:14.232
How... how does that
make you feel?

14:15.001 --> 14:16.502
I don't really like it.

14:16.569 --> 14:18.904
You-you kind of wish
the roles were reversed?

14:19.939 --> 14:21.407
A little bit, yeah.

14:21.474 --> 14:22.708
You got, like,
an emptiness in your stomach,

14:22.776 --> 14:24.410
a pit that you can't quite name?

14:24.477 --> 14:25.810
Maybe.

14:25.877 --> 14:29.013
That, my friend, is jealousy.

14:34.753 --> 14:36.321
Can I hold the duck
for a little bit?

14:36.388 --> 14:38.323
I'm sorry, no.

14:44.495 --> 14:45.429
Sweetie, you tried.

14:45.496 --> 14:46.630
That's the important thing.

14:46.698 --> 14:48.365
Yep, I tried and I failed.

14:48.433 --> 14:49.833
I told you I'm not you.

14:49.900 --> 14:51.968
Your problem is, you don't
see me for my imperfections.

14:52.036 --> 14:53.403
Please, not the Yoda
birthmark again.

14:53.471 --> 14:54.871
But it looks just like him.

14:54.939 --> 14:56.780
I'm saying that my big
ideas don't always work.

14:56.808 --> 14:59.475
I've had some spectacular
failures of my own.

14:59.543 --> 15:01.544
You know that pond
I've been helping

15:01.611 --> 15:03.579
to recover from
the environmental disaster?

15:03.647 --> 15:06.816
Well, that disaster
was all my fault.

15:06.883 --> 15:08.417
What are you talking about?

15:08.485 --> 15:10.319
It was back in the '80s.

15:10.387 --> 15:12.621
A large crowd had gathered
for what was being called

15:12.689 --> 15:14.823
the spectacular
to end all spectaculars.

15:14.890 --> 15:16.358
And the sponsor

15:16.425 --> 15:18.326
was America's favorite
saliva-powered candy:

15:18.394 --> 15:19.561
Pop Rocks.

15:19.628 --> 15:21.696
I poured tons and
tons of that stuff

15:21.764 --> 15:23.331
into that pond.

15:23.399 --> 15:24.999
I was hoping for maybe
a little fizzing, you know,

15:25.067 --> 15:26.300
a little crackling.

15:26.369 --> 15:27.635
No.

15:27.703 --> 15:28.770
It was a pink eruption.

15:28.838 --> 15:30.871
It was like a Pop Rock Pompeii.

15:30.938 --> 15:34.074
