15:34.141 --> 15:35.542
I remember seeing

15:35.610 --> 15:37.745
little kids covered in pink,
crying.

15:40.815 --> 15:41.882
And the noise, just...

15:43.685 --> 15:46.619
It was like
the devil's flatulence.

15:46.687 --> 15:48.621
Sales blew up.

15:48.689 --> 15:50.956
But so did a lot of the fish.

15:51.024 --> 15:53.826
My point is, baby,
I know failure.

15:53.894 --> 15:55.695
Thanks, Dad.

15:55.763 --> 15:56.763
You're welcome, kitten.

15:56.830 --> 15:58.330
Uh-oh.

15:58.399 --> 16:00.299
