the Windy City people.

16:00.367 --> 16:01.333
They are not happy.

16:01.401 --> 16:02.601
It's okay.

16:02.668 --> 16:04.002
We're gonna figure this out.

16:04.069 --> 16:05.003
Yes, we are!

16:05.070 --> 16:06.037
I believe in you!

16:06.105 --> 16:08.039
Check it out!
We're on TV.

16:08.107 --> 16:09.875
Christie Moon,
channel four news.

16:09.942 --> 16:11.877
We were hoping to get a few
words from the perpetrator,

16:11.944 --> 16:13.478
if you have a moment.
Uh, sorry...

16:13.546 --> 16:14.746
Yo, everybody, I'm famous!

16:14.814 --> 16:15.781
What, what!

16:15.848 --> 16:17.015
Oh, this just in:

16:17.082 --> 16:18.348
new footage of people fleeing.

16:18.417 --> 16:20.484
