16:20.552 --> 16:22.085
Everybody out of the way!

16:26.691 --> 16:29.927
It was like something
out of a horror movie.

16:35.599 --> 16:38.802
It was a
beautiful day in sunny Chicago.

16:38.869 --> 16:40.670
