Whoa!

16:50.613 --> 16:52.748
Run for your lives!

16:55.151 --> 16:57.018
Windy City Coffee.

16:57.086 --> 16:58.921
Dangerously good.

17:01.891 --> 17:04.358
That's what I'm talking about.

17:04.426 --> 17:05.693
Edgy, edgy.

