they're city ducks?

17:32.620 --> 17:34.420
Sorry, Andrew, but it's time.

17:34.489 --> 17:35.822
I'm gonna miss you, little guy.

17:35.890 --> 17:38.591
I'm gonna miss you, too.

17:38.658 --> 17:40.960
Said the duck.
Ah.

17:42.028 --> 17:43.462
Ladies and gentlemen,

17:43.530 --> 17:44.797
