17:51.938 --> 17:54.138
declaring it just another
candy-related catastrophe

17:54.206 --> 17:56.941
like the gobstopping
of the Chicago River in '82,

17:57.009 --> 17:59.076
or the Nerd melt of '81.

18:01.013 --> 18:02.814
But today is proof
of what happens

18:02.882 --> 18:05.617
if you dare to dream big
and work small.

18:05.684 --> 18:09.020
There were days I didn't know
if we'd succeed.

18:09.087 --> 18:11.488
But if I've learned
one thing in this life,

18:11.556 --> 18:13.089
there's no shame in failing.

18:13.157 --> 18:14.958
The only shame

18:15.026 --> 18:17.127
